So, the problem ist, that your list is only 5 numbers long and you do the empty check only before the first Players turn.

In the last run of the while loop, the first player gets the last number and without a check, the second player asks for his number, but now the list is empty...

To fix this, you have to put a empty check before the second player gets his number:

    System.out.println(list);
    if (list.isEmpty()) {
